MAVERICK 

21. Trail West to Fury   2/16/1958
Stranded during a flood, the brothers Maverick relate to pal Dandy Jim Buckley the story of why they cannot return to their home in Texas.

Stars James Garner as Bret Maverick and Jack Kelley as Bart Maverick
Guest star: Efrem Zimbalist Jr. (Dandy Jim Buckley) , Mike Hagen (1st Johnny Reb), Russ Bender (Doctor), Paul Fiero (Miguel), Charles Fredericks (Jesse Haden), Don Kelly (Jett), Gene Nelson (Jim Hewlit), Aline Towne (Laura Miller), Paul Savage (Tall Man)
